But in this one has to understand that it’s
all done just to express the Dhanesh Shakti

01:00:31.770 --> 01:00:36.470
of the Mother, just that She loves to give.

01:00:36.470 --> 01:00:42.409
She loves to give.

01:00:42.409 --> 01:00:47.899
Just out of joy that I had in Hampstead, I
felt I should now give you something.

01:00:47.899 --> 01:00:56.699
It’s beautiful there and that’s how we
have today tried to make some arrangement

01:00:56.699 --> 01:00:59.710
for that kind of a thing.

01:00:59.710 --> 01:01:10.649
So just before the puja I wanted to announce
this and then we can have the puja – very

01:01:10.649 --> 01:01:18.720
simple one, because today is a day of simplicity
– complete surrendering.

01:01:18.720 --> 01:01:33.740
Just imagine that these two colours are in
the Void, green and yellow, and if you mix

01:01:33.740 --> 01:01:38.649
them what is the colour you get?

01:01:38.649 --> 01:01:40.360
Green and yellow?

01:01:40.360 --> 01:01:42.629
You get the blue.

01:01:42.629 --> 01:01:47.470
So the green is the Nature.

01:01:47.470 --> 01:01:52.300
So an avadhuta has to become one with the
Nature.

01:01:52.300 --> 01:01:58.929
This is the sign of the Surya nadi, the Sun.

01:01:58.929 --> 01:02:07.780
That means an avadhuta has to be brilliant
like the Sun, brilliant like the Sun, and

01:02:07.780 --> 01:02:12.679
that detached as the Sun is.

01:02:12.679 --> 01:02:14.419
All the detachment must come into him.

01:02:14.419 --> 01:02:18.349
He need not have liver on Sun line.

01:02:18.349 --> 01:02:22.810
He will not have liver if he knows what to
eat and what not to eat.

01:02:22.800 --> 01:02:37.560
Normally all these gurus ate fruits, and they
ate meat, never fats and that’s how they

01:02:37.690 --> 01:02:39.333
kept their liver alright.

01:02:39.536 --> 01:02:49.117
This is, these are the two combinations which
are there in the Void.

01:02:49.117 --> 01:02:53.867
And the combination of these two, when they
combine, it makes a blue.

01:02:53.867 --> 01:02:54.867
What is the blue?

01:02:54.867 --> 01:02:55.867
Is the water.

01:02:55.867 --> 01:02:57.466
So, in the water.

01:02:57.466 --> 01:03:03.006
Now see the Gurus are surrounding the Lakshmi
on the Nabhi.

01:03:03.006 --> 01:03:08.786
On the Nabhi is the Lakshmi is in the centre
and they are surrounding her.

01:03:08.786 --> 01:03:10.796
They are her beauty.

01:03:10.796 --> 01:03:14.726
Without vairAgnya, without ascetic temperament,
the Lakshmi has no meaning.

01:03:14.726 --> 01:03:16.041
It has no meaning.

01:03:16.166 --> 01:03:19.431
It is expressed in giving, is giving.

01:03:19.571 --> 01:03:26.111
That is what it means, that without vairAgnya
the Lakshmi has no meaning.

01:03:26.141 --> 01:03:31.011
Without the feeling of giving Lakshmi has
no meaning.

01:03:31.031 --> 01:03:35.100
Why should Lakshmi come to anyone if they
do not want to give?

01:03:35.100 --> 01:03:40.483
And that is what one has to understand, is
the significance of giving.

01:03:40.553 --> 01:03:46.221
Now, today’s speciality is this, that: though
I am the Lakshmi – alright, I am the Mahalakshmi

01:03:46.221 --> 01:03:52.801
in everything – but I am also Vairagyi,
I am the detached.

01:03:52.801 --> 01:03:56.140
The One who is Nirmama, is beyond.

01:03:56.140 --> 01:03:59.430
Nobody can tie me, nobody can.

01:03:59.430 --> 01:04:01.620
Nothing can bound me.

01:04:01.620 --> 01:04:05.551
I just talk but it has no meaning, I am beyond.

01:04:05.551 --> 01:04:09.451
In the same way, all of you should try to
be beyond.

01:04:09.451 --> 01:04:16.780
So, from the Lakshmi angle I want to give
you something, because Lakshmi looks after

01:04:16.780 --> 01:04:19.780
the saints, and the saints have to be detached.

01:04:19.800 --> 01:04:24.610
That is the way it is going to work out.

01:04:24.670 --> 01:04:32.220
I hope you won’t go back and wear kashayas,
the orange robes (laughter).

01:04:32.220 --> 01:04:38.710
Discretion, discretion, has to mature.

01:04:38.750 --> 01:04:41.170
It’s the maturity of discretion now.

