Devo Maheshwara, Guru Sakshat Parabrahma,

01:07:06.764 --> 01:07:10.160
Shri Mataji Nirmala Ma, Tasmai Guruve namaha.

01:07:10.344 --> 01:07:13.460
Shri Mataji: You all know the meaning of this?

01:07:13.558 --> 01:07:17.360
Gurur Brahma, Gurur Vishnu, Gurur Devo Maheshwara.

01:07:17.619 --> 01:07:31.889
The Guru is the creator, Guru is the protector,
and Guru is the existence and the destroyer.

01:07:31.889 --> 01:07:45.829
Guru is the embodiment of the Parabrahma,
it’s the beyond state.

01:07:45.829 --> 01:07:53.599
And to such a Guru we bow.

01:07:53.599 --> 01:08:07.788
Just a little you can take it on your fingers
you can dip it, you see, and put it on your

01:08:07.788 --> 01:08:08.788
forehead, maybe.

01:08:08.788 --> 01:08:10.089
It’s a water which is now [vibrated].

01:08:10.089 --> 01:08:11.089
Haa!

01:08:11.089 --> 01:08:13.599
You will feel better.

01:08:13.599 --> 01:08:19.849
On the Sahasrara you can put it.

01:08:19.849 --> 01:08:26.548
Just sprinkle it all over you can.

01:08:26.548 --> 01:08:29.418
Let him do.

01:08:29.418 --> 01:08:34.438
Sprinkle it all over.

01:08:50.955 --> 01:08:54.555
Who are these?

01:08:54.625 --> 01:08:58.731
Maria is here.

01:08:58.776 --> 01:09:00.741
Yes.

01:09:00.771 --> 01:09:03.511
Jaldi karo! (hindi: do it quickly)

01:09:03.571 --> 01:09:09.661
Five people together should come forward – alright?

01:09:09.711 --> 01:09:10.910
Come along!

01:09:10.881 --> 01:09:11.751
Five of you.

01:09:11.841 --> 01:09:12.378
Yes.

01:09:12.487 --> 01:09:16.656
Come along!

01:09:43.921 --> 01:09:46.981
Get your finger into there and to my hand.

01:09:47.076 --> 01:09:51.065
Turn it like that, clockwise, with both the
hands.

01:09:51.065 --> 01:09:52.065
Alright.

01:09:52.065 --> 01:09:54.071
Now you rub your own hand.

01:09:54.131 --> 01:09:56.061
Now come along, you do it.

01:09:56.115 --> 01:09:58.065
Come along.

01:09:58.065 --> 01:10:00.024
Rub it.

01:10:00.024 --> 01:10:01.975
It’s good.
